    ("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_CVS_DIHYA_UA_DESCRIPTION",                             "Cities produce +5% [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production for each owned mountain tile when at war. Units receive +7 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength when fighting on owned desert tiles. When an enemy unit pillages one of your improvements, all enemy units on that tile and on adjacent tiles with the same owner are [ICON_DAMAGED] Damaged."),
